

PREREQUSITES
------------
PHP 4.x with GD library support (php4-gd)
MySQL 4.x
Database component of Sahana People registry system installed

INSTALLTION
-----------

1) Copy the graphs directory to your web root (e.g. /var/www)

2) Set the $webroot directory to point to the absolute path to graphs application (e.g. $webroot='/var/www/graphs')
   
   The files you need to modify are

    - $webroot/common/site@config.php
    - $webroot/common/container.php
    - @webroot/common/db@connect.php

3) Edit $webroot/site@config

   - Set the $docroot to point to the relative URL path to graphs application from the web server (e.g. $docroot='/graphs')
   - Set mySQL database login details 
   
   #-- database config --
   $host = "localhost";
   $dbuser="dbuser"; $dbpassword="dbpassword";

4) Install the Mambo mod_statistics module to include from within Mambo. 


